entries.journal_entry_description: Conduct a search of the Diktat's office at the capitol building.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Speak with the Corellian Diktat, Daclif Gallamby, and present the writs which authorize a search of his desk and data terminal.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Speak with the Diktat, Daclif Gallamby
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Search the Diktat's desk and personal papers on it.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Search the Diktat's data terminal and make note of any recent outbound communications.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: You found nothing even remotely incriminating or even suspicious among the Diktat's papers, data files, or recent communications. However you do find an odd device hooked into the Diktat's data terminal connection. Ask the Diktat if he knows what it is.
entries.task03_message_box_text: You found nothing even remotely incriminating or even suspicious among the Diktat's papers, data files, or recent communications. However you do find an odd device hooked into the Diktat's data terminal connection. Ask the Diktat if he knows what it is.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Ask the Diktat about the strange device you found hooked into his data terminal connection.
entries.task04_journal_entry_title: Ask the Diktat about the Strange Device
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Report to Lt. Jasper. Tell him that you did not find any evidence of wrongdoing, and then show him the device you found.
